$15 admission fee; $30 for dinner package - optional

* Please show up by 7:45 so we can purchase our tickets together *

You've seen our comics on HBO, Comedy Central and the Late Show With David Letterman. So come on out and enjoy our dinner packages, along with an incredible show!"

For more info, go to http://www.thecomedyc...

Starts at 8... should be done by 10. We can get drinks somewhere afterwards if people want.
